<div class="signature">
public string <b>$homeLink</b>;</div>

<p>the first hyperlink in the breadcrumbs (called home link).
If this property is not set, it defaults to a link pointing to <?php echo CHtml::link('CWebApplication::homeUrl', array('/site/doc', 'view' => 'CWebApplication', '#' => 'homeUrl')); ?> with label 'Home'.
If this property is false, the home link will not be rendered.</p>


